traits.locale_text: "Погодите-ка... это один из линейных служителей с палубы 67-3. Помню его, потому что он не из местных кланов, помогал мне перевозить пополнение экипажа с планеты. Что он тут делает?"

languages.text: "Wait... He's an operational officer from Deck 67-3. Not from one of the local clans, which is why I remember him. He helped me bring up the new recruits from the planet. What is he doing here?"

languages.text: 「待てよ…デッキ67-3の彼は管理責任者です。現地の氏族の者ではないのではっきりと覚えています。惑星から新兵を派遣するのを手伝ってくれました。こんな所で何をしているんだ？」
languages.original_text: "Wait... He's an operational officer from Deck 67-3. Not from one of the local clans, which is why I remember him. He helped me bring up the new recruits from the planet. What is he doing here?"

traits.locale_text: 「待てよ…デッキ67-3の彼は管理責任者だ。現地の氏族の者ではないのではっきりと覚えている。惑星から新兵を派遣するのを手伝ってくれた。ここで何をしているんだ？」

languages.text: “等等……他是67-3号甲板的操作员。他不是本地氏族的人，所以我才记得他。他曾协助过我从行星上招募新兵，可他在这里做什么呢？”
languages.original_text: "Wait... He's an operational officer from Deck 67-3. Not from one of the local clans, which is why I remember him. He helped me bring up the new recruits from the planet. What is he doing here?"

languages.text: «Un momento... es un oficial de operaciones de la cubierta 67-3. No es de los clanes locales, por eso le recuerdo. Me ayudó a subir a los reclutas nuevos del planeta. ¿Qué hace aquí?».
languages.original_text: "Wait... He's an operational officer from Deck 67-3. Not from one of the local clans, which is why I remember him. He helped me bring up the new recruits from the planet. What is he doing here?"

traits.locale_text: «Un momento... es un oficial de operaciones de la cubierta 67-3. No es de los clanes locales, por eso le recuerdo. Me ayudó a subir a los reclutas nuevos del planeta. ¿Qué hace aquí?».

languages.text: « Une seconde... C'est l'un des responsables des opérations du pont 67-3. Il n'appartient pas aux clans locaux, c'est pour ça que je me souviens de lui. Il m'a aidé à conduire les nouvelles recrues au vaisseau. Que fait-il ici ? »
languages.original_text: "Wait... He's an operational officer from Deck 67-3. Not from one of the local clans, which is why I remember him. He helped me bring up the new recruits from the planet. What is he doing here?"

traits.locale_text: « Une seconde... C'est l'un des responsables des opérations du pont 67-3. Il n'appartient pas aux clans locaux, c'est pour ça que je me souviens de lui. Il m'a aidé à conduire les nouvelles recrues au vaisseau. Que fait-il ici ? »

languages.text: "Moment ... das ist ein leitender Offizier von Deck 67-3. Er gehört nicht zu den lokalen Clans, darum erinnere ich mich an ihn. Er hat mir geholfen, die neuen Rekruten von dem Planeten raufzubringen. Was macht er hier?"
languages.original_text: "Wait... He's an operational officer from Deck 67-3. Not from one of the local clans, which is why I remember him. He helped me bring up the new recruits from the planet. What is he doing here?"

languages.text: "Bir saniye. Güverte 67-3'ten bir operasyon subayı bu. Yerel klanlardan değil, o yüzden hatırlayabildim. Gezegenden yeni askerler toplamama yardım etmişti. Burada ne yapıyor acaba?"
